{"tid":127084,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻兔仔忘記左自己兄弟！！！","createTime":"2017-02-19T23:36:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T07:41:44.000Z","uid":27099,"like":99,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af3d4b1d4e379afb5911b493998ab5dd56f1aac1","tid":127084,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T23:36:46.000Z","msg":"今日我兄弟走左　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />　留低左隻兔仔俾我　因為佢去加拿大　要個幾月先返黎　<br />\n<br />\n咁佢隻兔仔叫狗勁　我隻叫狗強　佢地係異父異母嘅親生兄弟黎<br />\n<br />\n咁我頭先搭的士時　就滿心歡喜咁幻想兩隻兔仔兄弟重逢　喜極而泣嘅時刻　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住返到屋企後　放狗勁出黎　籠入面嘅狗強感應到兄弟嘅氣息之後　竟然狂暴化！！！　以超高機動性＋強大物理破壞力暴走　咁我平時會用條鏈扣住個草波係個籠入面　廢事個草波掉左落兔仔廁所　點撚知狗強喪撞個草波　連條鐵鏈都整甩埋！！！　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　<br />\n<br />\n我心諗：一定係兄弟重逢　倍感激動　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　然後我又放狗強出黎　狗強即以快如雷電嘅速度　排除萬難高速接近狗勁！！！　點知　點知！！！<br />\n<br />\n狗強竟然同狗勁扑野！！！　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　仲要條細JJ　係對撚住狗勁個頭　我屌！！！　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　其實狗強狗勁第一日相遇時都有發生過呢種事　當時係狗勁騎狗強　（當時狗勁體型大過狗強）　但今日狗強已經肥過狗勁好多　我諗係品種問題　又可能同我老豆成日餵佢食大力菜有關　我諗係狗強回想起當日嘅屈辱　今日恃勢凌人作出報復　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　<br />\n<br />\n之後狗勁都覺醒埋　突然反撲　騎返狗強轉頭　我心諗：我屌　做咩兄弟要搞基　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後大戰左幾個回合後　雙方好似終於發現到對方都有細JJ　原來係男仔後　就分開左幾分鐘　之後狗強突然又爆速跑向狗勁　我以為又要世界大戰抹黑宇宙了嘅時候　狗強係狗勁咁隔離平排扒低左　個表情好似講緊：咦　原來係兄弟黎　頭先SOR喎　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　<br />\n<br />\n宜家狗勁去邊　狗強都跟住　果然血脈相連嘅兄弟情係無野可以改變得到　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我媽媽都話：哇　呢隻（狗勁）咁乖嘅　個死仆街（狗強）日日發神經　不如食左佢好過啦　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我老豆就好出奇咁行近狗勁　抱起佢　話：咦　佢係咪病左　點解可以抱？　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　（因為狗強係從來唔俾人抱的　單手摸已經係極限）<br />\n<br />\n最後結論係兩隻又和平相處啦　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930103675462050379a5684788a49795ee391f78","tid":127084,"uid":75556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T00:09:35.000Z","msg":"Hello 冇圖"},{"pid":"ac700d89ab68b2db45a28791912b40004a19fddf","tid":127084,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"狗強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b6ed73a9c79f0e0d4006b896f07790d581cda5","tid":127084,"uid":65931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見到狗強POST<br />\n好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e533ce702e7d9f08946f3673fbff6a795a910d93","tid":127084,"uid":2211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:08:01.000Z","msg":"無圖？"},{"pid":"2672b142e487840c0376f447ae49a04341702502","tid":127084,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"之前追狗強狗勁po笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9045d270f8e55c6639494047cc9377d93aa7fdd1","tid":127084,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:17:32.000Z","msg":"好掛住狗強"},{"pid":"64c6e